  "description": [
    "Friday July 4 1947 Jewish Vets Fight Back We wonder what the British Jews are saying about those Jewish war veterans breaking up meetings of British fascists actually by force of knuckles Os course before they resort to the use of mus cular Judaism they expose the war records or rather the lack of any decent war records of the fascists soap boxers Most of them according to these veterans of Dunkirk and Arnheim are former Mosleytites and have records of British patriotism that should put them behind the bars of any decent country Yet we can see some of our staid and conservative British Jewry deplore with hands raised in holy horror the fact of Jews actually taking the law in their own hands as it is said We deplore lawlessness in any form We deplore it more when it enters our life in the form of lawful freedom of speech And because we deplore such lawful lawlessness as is perpetrated by the fascistsprotected by an apathetic police that we feel the Jewish war veterans of Great Britain are not actually taking the law in their own hands They are PROTECTING THE LAW upholding their right of life and"
  ],
